{"tid":2189104,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買咗tesla嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2020-09-04T15:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T15:58:32.000Z","uid":345051,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"465862fa6d8e8adc996c6078f1266797e4461e9e","tid":2189104,"uid":345051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:58:32.000Z","msg":"我哋一齊祈禱<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">唔好輸呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們在美國的父，願人都尊你的名為鋼鐵俠，願你的space X降臨，願你的tesla，行在地上，如同starlink行在天上。我們晚晚炒的美股，今日分拆給我們；接上我們的大腦，如同我們接上電腦的接口。不要叫我們遇見熊市，救我們脫離貧窮；因為火星，地球，月球，全是你的，直到永遠。阿門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A383afz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA383afz.jpg&h=bcda5461&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}